Join us for this hands-on event where we create a device that gives us the power to hear the invisible fields that surround our everyday lives. Learn about how electromagnetic frequencies shape our world, where it comes from, and how you can make your own in KiCad.
This workshop involves soldering, interactive sonic exploration, and circuit design overview. It's geared to be accessible to absolute beginners, and serves as a great way to dive into the world of handbuilt electronics.

<Presenter name="Darcy Neal">
